<!-- note that index will be the about page -->
<Layout title="About Page">
  <section id="about">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/Headshot.jpg" alt="Kobe Prior" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-bio">
        <h1>Kobe Prior</h1>
        <p class="bio-location">Golden, CO &mdash; Colorado School of Mines</p>
      <p>
          I’m an Electrical Engineer from 
          <a href="https://www.mines.edu/" target="_blank" class="inline-link">
              Colorado School of Mines
          </a> 
          currently pursuing my Master’s Thesis program, which I expect to complete in May 2027. 
          My professional interests include signal processing, communications, and antenna systems. 
          I’ve had the opportunity to conduct hands-on research in the 
          <a href="https://arc.elsherbeni.com/" target="_blank" class="inline-link">
              Antennas, RFID, and Computational Electromagnetics (ARC)
          </a> 
          group under 
          <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=B3mIYBMAAAAJ&hl=en" target="_blank" class="inline-link">
              Atef Elsherbeni
          </a>, 
          while also gaining industry experience through internships at 
          <a href="https://www.rincon.com/" target="_blank" class="inline-link">
              Rincon Research Corporation
          </a> 
          and 
          <a href="https://www.zai.com/" target="_blank" class="inline-link">
              Zeta Associates
          </a>. 
          Along the way, I’ve been honored with multiple Dean’s List recognitions and the 
          Outstanding Graduating Senior Award—achievements I’m proud of, but that only represent 
          the beginning of what I hope to accomplish in the field.
      </p>
        <a href="/Resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="resume-link"
          >View My Resume →</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
